last_resistance.instructions:
Gameplay:

Collect resources for your High Score by shoot down the UFOs.
You need Resources for your bullets otherwise its over.
Every round increased the number of UFOs.
You get damage when a UFO attacked you and the vehicle conditions is going down. (0 = game over)
You have assistants and they can repair you, when you stand by them for 5 seconds.
If a UFO attacked your assistants, they lose morale and the Human Resistance is going down. You lost your assistans when the Human Resistance reached 0.
You get bonus resources and morale when you make a 5x, 10x, 15x, 20x or 25x combo. So you can get new assistants, push the Human Resistance and make more resources for your High Score.







Controls:

Move your vehicle with your mouse.
Shoot with Left-Click.
Pause with P or B
Quit with Q or E (Abort the round)
Press and hold ctrl or Spacebar to view the options.
last_resistance.description:
Fight our last battle and defend the humanity against the alien invaders. Classic arcade gameplay




Story:

For decades we have been looking for intelligent life on other planets. But then it found us first!
Thus began a bitter war between aliens and humans for power over resources, research units and the sheer survival of their civilization. It turned out that the invaders were more intelligent than hoped for and so they took after a short time the upper hand in the battle for the planet and its inhabitants.
Nevertheless, there is a small group of survivors who called themselves Last Resistance and they doesnt given up. You are the vehicle commander of this group and responsible for the defense of the presumably last stand against the prevailing aliens. While there are a few brave people who are actively assist you in the defense, but secretly everyone is clear about one thing: This fight is hopeless!
Scouts have reported that several UFOs have already set a course to the camp and they will arrive shortly. Stand up for a hard and bitter fight. He will grant no breaks, and only ends when the last defense collapses.


Unlockable Contents:

You can unlock 3 simple Standard skins, 1 new vehicle and a new difficulty mode.
Look at the category Unlock Progress for more informations about it.
Hardcore mode:
You earn significantly more resources.
You suffer significantly more damage.
More enemies.

burrows and smash them all before your time dissolves to
zero. Reward yourself with more burrows in each level and
have infinite fun through the numerous levels.

burrows.

3_pandas_brazil.instructions: Use the mouse to move the pandas through each level.

Make sure you have all the ingredients because you cant just improvise on a special cake like this. Even though it may seem to be just a simple chocolate cake if you shape it like a heart the person you are serving it to will know you care and that you put a lot of passion in the cooking process. Enjoy this fun cooking game and make sure you try out our recipe on your significant other. Have fun!

Be careful how you drive so you do not crash and if you want to get as many points as possible be very fasty and collect stars. When you reach the end of the line, try to destroy the tower by shooting at them, which will require some excellent skills from your part. Besides the parking skills and the crane handling ones, you will also get to experience a great new mini game! Just do not crash into anything and complete your mission before the time runs out. Enjoy eight intense levels! Have a blast!

jurassic_jeep_madness.instructions: Use your arrow keys to drive and the X key to activate turbo.
jurassic_jeep_madness.description: You find yourself caught in a Jurassic land full of dangerous dinosaurs who are constantly attacking your jeep. There are eight very exciting levels that are available for you to play and you can submit your score to compare it with the other players. Have a great time playing this fun game!

lucky_irish_frenzy.instructions: Use your arrow keys to drive and your X key to activate turbo.

Use your turbo power when you need it and pick up four leaf clovers to fill up your bar. Make sure to keep your balance and do not crash! Have a great time playing all eight levels!

cooking_wedding_cake.author: Smileycooking

police_station_parking_2.description: Drive a police car and try to park it in front of the police station fast and safely. twin_delights_matching.description: Cokes, chips, burgers and cakes, all in doubles! For the mouth that waters, you must spot the pairs to win them all! Just give in and indulge because there are no calories here!
twin_delights_matching.name: Twin Delights Matching
twin_delights_matching.author: Yotreat.com

new_york_gangs.instructions: Use your arrow keys to drive, your space bar to brake and your X key to shoot.

possible color combos for maximum fun.

The cute little angel has descended on the garden to relax.

her, why don’t you add happiness and life to the serene

all possible color combos.

A donut is something more than just a delicious snack..it can make anyones day brighter or it can help you start your day fresh. Some people enjoy them with their morning coffee, others like them with creamy filling and some just like it plain. the formidable levels with different puzzle designs and
beat the timer to stand a class apart.
juicy_fruit_puzzles.name: Juicy Fruit Puzzles
juicy_fruit_puzzles.author: Fabsys

dodo_bird_challange.instructions: Click the mouse or use the space key in order to help the bird fly.
dodo_bird_challange.description:
Accept this great challenge and help Dodo Bird fly away safely from the glacial lands before he freezes!
He needs to reach the tropical lands without hitting any obstacle that might get in his way!
An easy game, great fun, just perfect to help time fly by!
Help him get as farther as he can before he freezes!
dodo_bird_challange.name: Dodo Bird Challange
dodo_bird_challange.author: ARPAmedia

zombudoy_2.instructions:
Use Mouse to Aim/Shoot
Press key 1 for Primary Gun
Press key 2 for Secondary Handgun
Press key 3 for Bombs
Press key 4 for Help Calls
Press key 5 for Bonus Gun (if you have one)
CONTROL for night vision
SPACE for zoom if weapon has sniper
zombudoy_2.description: Zombudoy is back again! and now they want to join this holiday. in Zombudoy 2 you can unlock 30+ different kinds of weapons, beat 20+ kinds of zombies, in this 40 level Christmas special zombie game
zombudoy_2.name: Zombudoy 2
zombudoy_2.author: Box10.com

bream_paper_cooking.description: To cook one the most enjoyable dish on your birthday party, bream paper with acticook will be a perfect one as this is tasty, delicious and easy to prepare. Lets give a try by following the instructions of the cooking game and complete the preparation. Share this recipe with your friends and have fun!
bream_paper_cooking.name: Bream paper cooking
bream_paper_cooking.author: Dressupkiss.com

underground_machines.instructions: Use your arrow keys, your X key to use NoS and your space bar to brake.
underground_machines.description: Understand the complex mechanism of a great workflow by taking turn to drive some powerful underground machines: a truck, a crane and a bus. In each level you will have a different mission to complete and you will have to drive your truck against time, to transport workers and ores, to collect ores in your crane, to pick up workers in a bus or to deliver ores to factories. There are nine amazing levels available! Have a great time playing Underground Machines!
underground_machines.name: Underground Machines
underground_machines.author: Idea Studios

delightful_granola_bars.description: There is many granola bars in the grocery and I specially love them when I dont have a lot of time to eat a snack. Play this wonderful cooking game and see how easy it is to make it.
delightful_granola_bars.name: Delightful Granola Bars
delightful_granola_bars.author: Yokogames.com

girls_on_wheels.instructions: Use arrow keys to balance and drive your bikes.
girls_on_wheels.description:
Race other girls in many intense levels.Use arrow keys to balance just right your selected bike and make it to the finish line first.After each 5 levels new bikes are unlock and new engines for a better performance of your bike.Improve your driving skills and if you manage to finish all 23 levels and you consider yourself a expert driver then tray the Expert mode where the speed of your rivals is increased.
Have fun and good luck!
girls_on_wheels.name: Girls On Wheels
girls_on_wheels.author: Vitalitygames.com

monster_truck_challenge.instructions: Use the up arrow to accelerate and the down to reverse. The left and right arrow keys alter the way you can climb or go down.
monster_truck_challenge.description: You need to get to the end of the track in the quickest time possible. Find the best way to navigate some of the what look like impossible boulders to get over. The foreground though covers some of the smaller boulders so you will have to edge forward carefully so that you do not flip your truck over and wreck the level.
monster_truck_challenge.name: Monster Truck Challenge
monster_truck_challenge.author: Online Games Area

amanda_goes_to_school.instructions: Use the mouse to help Amanda to choose her school uniforms and accessories.
amanda_goes_to_school.description: Our little girl Amanda is always excited when she goes to school. One of the reasons is because she can wear those cute school uniforms and use those girly accessories. She also loves changing her hairstyle and color.
amanda_goes_to_school.name: Amanda Goes To School
amanda_goes_to_school.author: Gameskiff

ice_cream_crazy.instructions: This game is played with mouse only.
ice_cream_crazy.description: Here you can find out how you can cook your own crazy ice cream, using milk, eggs, strawberry, vanilla cream and other delicious ingredients. Add some yummy decorations and there you have, a refreshing ice cream. Enjoy!
ice_cream_crazy.name: Ice Cream Crazy
ice_cream_crazy.author: Smileycooking

spongebob_fun_race.instructions: Use the arrow keys to play this game.
spongebob_fun_race.description: Join Spongebob in a new underwater racing game. A fun adventure in which he has to get as many stars as possible. Drive as good as you can, only in this way he will get a high score and win the game. Good Luck!
spongebob_fun_race.name: SpongeBob Fun Race
spongebob_fun_race.author: Smileycooking

girl_travels_the_world.description: If theres something that this lovely young lady loves most in this world, then it must be fashion and... traveling! Thats right, she never misses a vacation or just a few days off to go on a trip and visit a new city, a new island, a new... corner of the world. Right now shes getting ready for a shopping spree to... Paris, so how about helping her pick and pack only the most feminine chic outfits from her wardrobe, only the prettiest, the most exquisite accessories, too, that will help her put together some... effortlessly french chic fashion looks before hitting the streets of Paris
girl_travels_the_world.name: Girl Travels the World
girl_travels_the_world.author: Rainbowdressup
tags: travel dressup dress-up fashion trip Paris girls games

backyard_escape.instructions: Click on the objects around the place to add them to the inventory. Combine the objects in the inventory panel. Execute to escape out of the room.
backyard_escape.description: You got yourself stuck in a stranger’s garden. When you try to leave you notice that the garden does not have a keyhole. Find the possible and the quickest way to escape out of this garden.
backyard_escape.name: Backyard Escape
backyard_escape.author: Yotreat.com

santa_claus_cookies_recipe.description: Hello ladies! Its time for another one of our really delicious recipes! Since Christmas time is approaching really fast, we have thought about showing you how to prepare a really festive recipe. This delicious recipe is called Santa Claus Cookies Recipe, and will be taught to you by who else than our beloved Santa Claus He is really excited about having you as his guest and preparing together the delicious cookies.
santa_claus_cookies_recipe.name: Santa Claus Cookies Recipe
santa_claus_cookies_recipe.author: CuteZee

big_truck_parking_pro.instructions: move your truck with the arrow keys, space to brake and ctrl key to lift and put down boxes
big_truck_parking_pro.description: Think you are the best driver Test your skills trying to maneuver  both a truck and a forklift with boxes. This game is made for highly skilled drivers that can drive a truck full of boxes on the narrow roads of the city.
big_truck_parking_pro.name: Big Truck Parking Pro
big_truck_parking_pro.author: SportGamesArena

hobo_6_hell.instructions:
A to punch and pick up objects
S for kicks and stuff
Arrow keys to move
hobo_6_hell.description: Our dearest Hobo has died and gone to hell! He now needs to face hordes of demons and their master Satan. This should be all in a days work for Hobo!
hobo_6_hell.name: Hobo 6 HELL
hobo_6_hell.author: Flash Game Submitter

truck_parking_mania.instructions: Use arrow keys to drive your truck
truck_parking_mania.description: Choose one of three trucks and drive them to designated parking area. Avoid various objects and moving cars. Try not to hit any crates because theyll damage you severely. Park your truck before time expires and try to finish all the levels.
truck_parking_mania.name: Truck Parking Mania
truck_parking_mania.author: Bestparkinggames.com

beach_kids_differences.instructions:
Click on the differences to spot them and complete the game
before you lose time. Aware of wrong clicks since you might
lose preciously earned points.
beach_kids_differences.description:
Kids are seems to be playing joyfully on the shore with
marshy sand by enjoying the cool breeze. Go with these kids
and double the joy of the moment by spotting the
difference.
beach_kids_differences.name: Beach Kids Differences
beach_kids_differences.author: Fabsys

dinner_date.description: Youve just got hired at one of the newly opened luxurious restaurants in town, lucky you! Now, make sure you make the best first impression by attending to all the customers coming in to enjoy their lovely, highly romantic dates here, in a cozy stylish ambiance. Be efficient when it comes to carrying out their orders and make sure you dont spoil these couples special evenings by leaving them waiting too long or...  messing up their orders!
dinner_date.name: Dinner Date
dinner_date.author: Rainbowdressup
tags: management simulation skill food restaurant serving games girls online

the_rock_vs_john_cena_slapathon.description: We all love wrestling and it is time to take two all stars from the wrestling world and put them in the ring together: The Rock vs John Cena! You will have to choose sides so pick your victim and slap it with a ladder or a chair until you run out of moves. You will have to get as much speed as you can to get a great score! This is a real fun game where you can compare your score with your friends. Have a blast!
the_rock_vs_john_cena_slapathon.name: The Rock Vs John Cena Slapathon
the_rock_vs_john_cena_slapathon.author: Idea Studios

fast_food_management.description: You create your own fast food company and you have to serve some hot dogs, burgers, pops and more. This is your day opening and you will have many new customer because of that. Enjoy your grand opening.
fast_food_management.name: Fast Food Management
fast_food_management.author: Yokogames.com

rescue_kiba_turkish.description: Kiba & Kumba, the popular monkey couple best known from KaiserGames games network (SpielAffe / KralOyun / KibaGames ...), are now finally starring in their own entire game! Monkey lady Kiba has been hijacked by an evil villain, which brings Monkey King Kumba to the scene. Ready for rescueing his girlfriend. Accompany him on his adventure through various worlds, which will amaze you!
rescue_kiba_turkish.name: Rescue Kiba Turkish
rescue_kiba_turkish.author: Kaiser-Games-GmbH

red_flight.instructions: Use the Left and Right arrow keys to move. Use the Up arrow key to do a Thunder attack.
red_flight.description: Your job as a police officer of the future is to clear the streets of the rebel forces. They are driving at you head on and with many of their recruits. Shoot em up!
red_flight.name: Red Flight
red_flight.author: Slix media

urban_mayhem_truck.instructions: Use your arrow keys to drive, your space bar to brake, use the left and right keys to maintain balance.
urban_mayhem_truck.description: Take down the town with Urban Mayhem Truck. Create chaos and disorder with your pro driving skills in this uphill racing game. Be dangerous and be confident in your extreme driving skills! Today you got the chance to choose and ride your awesome monster truck in this action racing game! Drive around 8 crazy levels crushing cars, running over trucks, launching off ramps and demolishing everything until you get to the finish line.
urban_mayhem_truck.name: Urban Mayhem Truck
urban_mayhem_truck.author: Idea Studios

angry_bee.description: Help the Angry Bee shoot all the yellow honeycombs from the screen. Use the different coloured combs for special attacks and be sure to destroy every last yellow one in each of the 20 levels.
angry_bee.name: Angry Bee
angry_bee.author: Kaiser-Games-GmbH

ninja_panda_couple.instructions: Use arrow keys and asdw to move
ninja_panda_couple.description: Can you beat this training course and become a full fledged ninja panda either on 1 player or on a 2 player mode with your panda wife Addictive, fun platformer everyone can enjoy.
ninja_panda_couple.name: Ninja Panda Couple
ninja_panda_couple.author: 5games.com

hanas_gym.description: Welcome to the new Hana adventure and his new time management game. This time you will help her to manage a gym fitness, assist and guide the clients to preferred machineries, make them happy while keeping them in fitness. Good-luck!
hanas_gym.name: Hanas Gym
hanas_gym.author: JAPMedia

oppa_caishen_style.instructions:
Use the Arrow Keys or WSAD to move.
Esc to Pause
oppa_caishen_style.description: CaiShen Ye, the Chinese God of Wealth has put the Fake Psy to the ultimate test. The Chinese New Year Gangnam Style game features lion dancers, crackers and a fearsome dragon. Collect the red packets and gold... Oppa CaiShen Style.
oppa_caishen_style.name: Oppa CaiShen Style
oppa_caishen_style.author: Tamugaia

blocks.instructions:
Move the blocks in one line to make them disappear until any block is left on the level.
“R” – Restart Level
“E” – Undo Last Action
“S” – Sound
“M” – Music
“Esc” – Menu
blocks.description: BLOCKS is a logic puzzle game with 100 levels to twist your brain. Move the blocks in one line to make them disappear until any block is left on the level. This game is a real challenge for your mind!
blocks.name: Blocks
blocks.author: Kongregate.com

madeline_hatters_tea_cookies.description: Madeline has some friends coming to the tea party she is having this afternoon, and is thinking about making some delicious cookies. Among her friends, there is one particular one, named Jessie that absolutely loves cookies, so those tea cookies must come out perfect! Madeline would be very grateful if you would help her prepare the delicious cookies in this exciting cooking game called Madeline Hatters Tea Cookies.
madeline_hatters_tea_cookies.name: Madeline Hatters Tea Cookies
madeline_hatters_tea_cookies.author: CuteZee

endless_war_5.instructions: WASD to move, Mouse to shoot, F,G – switch weapons, Q, E – switch turrets.
endless_war_5.description:
The fifth instalment of Endless War series brings you to a large scale tank warfare. You wouldn’t be able to control a singe soldier, instead you’ll be choosing from 11 different tanks, armored cars and self-propelled guns.
Prepare to face over 25 types of enemies, including tanks, pillboxes, infantry, cannons, howitzers and so on.
endless_war_5.name: Endless War 5
endless_war_5.author: Flash Game Submitter

my_dinosaur.description:
The dinosaurs are back. If you’ve always wanted your own dinosaur, this dream can finally come true with Kaisergames’ “My Dino”. Forget about Brontosaurus, Triceratops or Tyrannosaurus and create your very own unexplored species. Choose between a dangerous predator and a cute giant and let the creative juices flow. Did your dinosaur attack with razor sharp teeth or did it prefer to nibble on trees Was his back decorated with plates, did it have a curious head or was it formed efficiently without much clutter Nearly ten Million possible combinations set no boundaries for your fantasy. And even more, you may choose from an endless pool of colours and decorations.
Once your dinosaur has hatched, lead it to new lands decorated with other creatures and items, give it a unique name and impress your friends with your own majestic reptile.
my_dinosaur.name: My Dinosaur
my_dinosaur.author: Kaiser-Games-GmbH

candy_max.description:
Grow your Candy large and Bump into other Candies to reduce their size and win the game.
Hover over the Candy to increase the size and do not forget to move away before you come into contact with other candies.
candy_max.name: Candy Max
candy_max.author: Yotreat.com

glamour_girl.instructions: Use the mouse to click and choose the best outfit for this girl.
glamour_girl.description: You like being a glamorous girl and dressing like a lady Help this girl get ready for a glamorous party. Have fun creating different outfits and choosing the right accessories for the look!
glamour_girl.name: Glamour Girl
glamour_girl.author: Gameskiff

italy_rally.instructions: Use the arrow keys to play this game.
italy_rally.description: Take a tour of Italy, get photos of the most famous places. Today you can visit them by traveling with a big and fast truck. Also as you will go throw each level, try your best to collect as many points you can and win the Italy rally championship!
italy_rally.name: Italy Rally
italy_rally.author: Smileycooking

parking_in_style.instructions: Use your arrow keys to drive and the space bar to brake.
parking_in_style.description: Park your stylish car in the big city, making sure you do not crash it or that you will not hit the pedestrians. Use your arrow keys to drive and your space bar to brake and try to carefully park your car in the highlighted spot. Be very fast, because if the time runs out you may lose. There are eight fun levels for you to try out. Have a blast!
parking_in_style.name: Parking In Style
parking_in_style.author: Idea Studios

new_york_pizza.instructions: This game is played with mouse only.
new_york_pizza.description: Today we are going to Manhattan where we are going to eat a pizza at one of the most famous Restaurants of New York. Join the game and see for yourself how you can cook a yummy New York Pizza. Take different ingredients like flower, yeast, tomato sauce, pepperoni slices and all other delicious ingredients you like to make the most tasty pizza.
new_york_pizza.name: New York Pizza
new_york_pizza.author: Smileycooking

strawberry_toffee_tart.description: Good new, ladies! Today we are going to have the unique opportunity to learn how to prepare a really exciting and delicious recipe. This fabulous dessert is called Strawberry Toffee Tart, and ever since I was a little girl, my mother used to prepare it for me every time I was feeling a little bit sad. Before you will be able to get started on the preparation of this recipe, the first thing that you will have to do will be to make sure that you do have all the necessary ingredients. Have a really fantastic time playing our brand new cooking game called Strawberry Toffee Tart. Have fun!
strawberry_toffee_tart.name: Strawberry Toffee Tart
strawberry_toffee_tart.author: CuteZee

Disappearing Path.description: Create a path to guide the ball to the flag in each level, but hurry - the path won't stay for long!
Disappearing Path.name: Disappearing Path

parking_in_the_hamptons.instructions: Use arrow keys or WASD keys to control the car and Space bar to brake.
parking_in_the_hamptons.description: Take a chance and see if you could handle a luxurious life by parking a nice car in the Hamptons. Do not crash it because you will have to restart the level. Use your arrow keys or your WASD keys to control it and you space bar to brake. Also take notice of time, as it is limited. Try to complete all twelve levels with the highest score possible! Enjoy!
parking_in_the_hamptons.name: Parking in the Hamptons
parking_in_the_hamptons.author: Idea Studios

hanas_pet_shop.description: A new episode with you preferred heroine and we need you again in this new adventure. This time you will help Hana into a new pet shop in your city. Take care of each animals and serve the clients as best as you can. Animals need health care and some customers will buy foods or animals from your supermarket. Make a lot of money and buy new care for the pet shop.
hanas_pet_shop.name: Hanas Pet Shop
hanas_pet_shop.author: JAPMedia

squishy_friends_quest.description: There are lots of squishy cute octopuses in the sea but they are all sad for they cannot find their pair. Put on your explorers hat and help these octopus to find their pair.
squishy_friends_quest.name: Squishy Friends Quest
squishy_friends_quest.author: Fabsys

chicken_general_tso.description: This is a new trend to eat chicken general tso and everybody love it. This is so sweet and tender that I would eat it everyday. Learn how to cook this new trend with this new game.
chicken_general_tso.name: Chicken General Tso
chicken_general_tso.author: Yokogames.com

sweetland.instructions: Use the arrow keys to rotate the world.
sweetland.description: Welcome to Sweetland, a delicious world filled full of candy! Rotate the world and use the gravity to help guide your friend to the exit while avoiding traps and collecting 3 stars!
sweetland.name: Sweetland
sweetland.author: Box10.com

robot_go_home.instructions:
Use mouse to interact with objects.
Click robot to move, click again to stop.
robot_go_home.description: Help this lost little robot find his way home. Make your way through this puzzle, point and click adventure. Navigate through electric beans, lifts and more in order to help the robot get home
robot_go_home.name: Robot Go Home
robot_go_home.author: Box10.com

adventures_of_harry.instructions: Click the left mouse button to use the propeller.
adventures_of_harry.description: Guide Harry the mouse through 30 levels. Use the propeller by pressing the left mouse button to let him fly. Collect all 3 pieces of cheese in order to submit your fastest time. Watch out for the sharp obstacles that can pop the balloon. Nice cartoon style graphics and 30 challenging levels.
adventures_of_harry.name: Adventures of Harry
adventures_of_harry.author: Nowgamez.com

baltimore_sandwich_shop.instructions: Watch the bubble over the customer head and drag the ingredients in the same order and deliver them to the customer. Mistakes are alright, but should be dragged to the bin. Keep customers happy and never miss any of them. Do collect money, from happy customers and meet the target to play the next level.
baltimore_sandwich_shop.description: Baltimore Sandwich Shop is hiring people, guys! And this is not just another sandwich joint. If you are adept in handling many customers at a short span of time, without messing customer orders, no matter what crowd, you are supposed to be here.
baltimore_sandwich_shop.name: Baltimore Sandwich Shop
baltimore_sandwich_shop.author: Yotreat.com

battlefield_medic.instructions:
Accelerate - Up
Tilt - Left/Right Arrow
X - Use Rocket engine(when equipped)
battlefield_medic.description: During World War 2 the medics on the battlefield had to get supplies to and from battle during some of the worst battles ever. Now is your chance to show your ability to get to your destination. Upgrade your car with better engines, wheels, fuel, armor and more in order to fight your way through enemy forces.
battlefield_medic.name: Battlefield Medic
battlefield_medic.author: Box10.com

graffiti_time.instructions:
WASD,Arrows- control
Space- paint
R- restart
L- go to levels Menu
graffiti_time.description:
Sneak through the city by night and paint on cars without getting detected by the police.

As soon you are finished you can pick up a golden key and enter the spray can rocket to the next level. Much fun!
graffiti_time.name: Graffiti Time
graffiti_time.author: Miniduck.ru
tags: graffiti pixel street night spray color police cops

zombies_ate_juggles.instructions: Move your player via the arrow keys, or the WASD keys. Shoot with space bar. Strafe side-to-side or up-and-down by holding a Shift key. Change weapon with the 1,2,3,4 keys.
zombies_ate_juggles.description: Welcome to Clown Town full of zombies! Protect Juggles, the Clown Town mascot from an outbreak of zombie clowns, evil knife-throwing dolls, werewolves and more! Use your various weapons and complete all levels.
zombies_ate_juggles.name: Zombies Ate Juggles
zombies_ate_juggles.author: NowGamez

halloween_escape_abigail_lair.instructions: Use the objects in the house and combine them together to solve the puzzle or a clue to open the door. Be fast for Abigail may come back any time soon.
halloween_escape_abigail_lair.description: Abigail has kidnapped you for a human sacrifice and has left the house for some ceremony preparation this is a great opportunity escape but the door is bewitched. Find the way to break the spell and escape before Abigail comes back.
halloween_escape_abigail_lair.name: Halloween Escape Abigail Lair
halloween_escape_abigail_lair.author: Yotreat.com

need_water.instructions: See the in-game tutorial, use your mouse to dig through the ground (click and drag).
need_water.description: Need Water is a new challenging game like the where is my water game. Dig through the ground and try to get the water (and oil) to the factories. Destroy stones and control the liquids. The water should be guided to the water factory and the oil to the oil factory. Collect the diamonds that are hidden in the earth and buy new skills and items in the upgrade panel. Unlock the achievements and earn rewards. Try to complete all the challenging levels.
need_water.name: Need Water
need_water.author: Nowgamez.com

barbecue_contest.description: Compete against the computer to make delicous barbecues. Choose the correct food to finish your barbecue before your opponent does.
barbecue_contest.name: Barbecue Contest
barbecue_contest.author: Flobzoo.com

3d_flash_racer.instructions: Use the arrow keys to drive.
3d_flash_racer.description: Start racing with your vintage race car that you discovered among other ones in your uncles garage. After you cleaned the dust and got it into the repair shop you enter a racing competition since you remember your uncle saying this car was as fast as flash lightning. Its time to find out if thats true!
3d_flash_racer.name: 3D Flash Racer
3d_flash_racer.author: Cartitans.com
